Normalization techniques are used in processing a dataset to ensure all features contribute equally to a datapoint.

Batch Normalization was proposed to reduce the covariant in the distribution of the data which allows faster learning rate and convergence when training a neural network.























**Reference: Batch Normalization: Accelerating Deep Network Training by Reducing Internal Covariate Shift. https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.1502.03167**

